data.description: Welcome to your charming new haven, a cozy home where every detail has been lovingly updated to create a space that feels both modern and inviting. Picture yourself walking on the new flooring that stretches across each room, lending a fresh and homey feel! The interior and exterior have been painted with colors that soothe and welcome, while the light fixtures have been carefully chosen to add a touch of warmth. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is a delight with new cabinets and beautiful butcher block counters that invite you to cook and create. Both the secondary bathroom and the newly added primary bathroom en-suite, complete with a large walk-in shower and a double vanity, have been designed for comfort and relaxation. Imagine starting your days sitting on the adorable front porch, sipping your morning coffee while enjoying the peacefulness of the large front yard on this corner lot. And when you're ready for some outdoor adventure, Jones Brothers Park and the beautiful Lake Travis are just a short walk or drive away, offering the perfect escape into nature. And the best part, no HOA! This home isn’t just a place to live; it’s a cozy retreat, a corner of the world just for you and your loved ones. Come and see how life can be both comfortable and exciting in this lovely home!
